Ugthanki meat is food that may be obtained by cooking raw ugthanki meat, granting 40 experience when successful. Players may burn the meat while cooking, resulting in burnt meat. The burn rate while cooking these will decrease as players reach higher Cooking levels.

Ugthanki meat may be eaten to heal 3 Hitpoints or used to make an ugthanki kebab.

Compared to other cookable food, ugthanki meat has unusual burn rates. At levels up to 82, the chance to burn this meat is higher on a range than on a fire. In addition, despite having no requirement to cook one, it never stops burning altogether on a regular fire or range, even at level 99.

'''Ugthanki meat''' is [[food]] that may be obtained by cooking [[raw ugthanki meat]], granting 40 experience when successful. Players may burn the meat while cooking, resulting in [[burnt meat]]. The [[burn rate]] while cooking these will decrease as players reach higher Cooking levels.

Ugthanki meat may be eaten to heal 3 [[Hitpoints]] or used to make an [[ugthanki kebab]].

Compared to other cookable food, ugthanki meat has unusual [[burn rate]]s. At levels up to 82, the chance to burn this meat is higher on a [[range]] than on a [[fire]]. In addition, despite having no requirement to cook one, it never stops burning altogether on a regular fire or range, even at level 99.
